headline.print_headline: Bryan Brothers Reach Year-End Final in Style
headline.main: Bryan Brothers Reach Year-End Final in Style

lead_paragraph: Bob and Mike Bryan thrashed French duo Julien Benneteau and Edouard Roger-Vasselin 6-0 6-3 to reach the final of the ATP World Tour Finals on Saturday.
